<br>
An air nuke that does a short term stun or interrupt...<br>
An earth nuke that does a short term root...<br>
An ice nuke that delivers a stackable 10% de-haste...<br>
A fire nuke that delivers a stackable resist debuff...<br>
<br>
These could all have damage values of 0 and only minor effects on their own, but could still be quite useful without stepping on toes as long as the resist rate is sane.<br>
<br>
I just don't think the magician solution lies in stronger nukes.  Stronger pets?  Yes.  More diverse offensive spells?  Sure.<br>
